I"~<p>We are an active research group at the <a href="https://www.uit.edu.vn/">University of Information Technology</a>. Our aim is to blends theory and system research focusing on developing Secure and Intelligent Services for IoT underlying several AI or Machine Learning methods, and their applications to industrial domains, such as the IT infrastructure industries and Smart City.</p>

